Factory and the factory's residential quarters to see laid-off
workers.
</P>
<P>
It is imperative to lay off some surplus workers so as to
achieve greater economic efficiency as a way to revitalize
state-owned enterprises, said the vice premier, who also called
for understanding from all sides.
</P>
<P>
Zhu said that the temporary difficulties of the state-owned
enterprises should be solved soon, and a modern enterprise system
will be established in the near future.
</P>
<P>
