<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, December 30 (Xinhua) -- The whole Hengfeng-Nanping
Railway line was joined today. As one of the nation's key
construction projects, the railway is expected to be an important
part of the transportation network in east China.
</P>
<P>
