Diana ranging from the regal princess wearing a tiara to more
recent casual poses.
</P>
<P>
Diana's family had been reluctant for stamps to go on sale
immediately after her death on August 31, thus delaying the issue.
</P>
<P>
The Post Office expects an unprecedented demand from the public
as well as collectors all over the world.
</P>
<P>
Several other countries have already issued stamps to
commemorate Diana. 
