<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 30 (Xinhua) -- The Bank of China and Air
China has jointly issued a new card, the Great Wall-Air China
Card, in Beijing.
</P>
<P>
The card will be also issued in Shanghai, Tianjin, Guangzhou
and Shenzhen and be gradually introduced in Dalian, Qingdao,
Xiamen, Chengdu, Nanjing, Xi'an, Fuzhou, Harbin and Hohhot, said
today's China Daily.
</P>
