airplane tickets from the ticket offices designated by Air China
as well as life accidental insurance up to 200,000 yuan (24,000 US
dollars).
</P>
<P>
The Bank of China has issued 7.48 million Great Wall cards
since its first issuance in 1986 and the deposits of the cards
have reached 18.9 billion yuan (2.28 billion US dollars).
</P>
<P>
Air China is the country's leading air carrier with its
passenger and freight transportation volume ranking the first.
